  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-02-07",
    "date": "2022-05-23T12:48:34Z",
    "text": "Unmask Our Kids Act\n\nThis bill prohibits a local educational agency (LEA) from receiving federal funds unless (1) in-person instruction is available to all students at each public elementary and secondary school under the jurisdiction of the LEA, and (2) a parent of a student at any school may opt out of a student face covering requirement."
